name: 3-Housing Price Analytics Report
content:
Reporting & Insights.


This report provides a structured summary of housing data analysis, including:

  • Data Quality Review : Highlights missing values, outliers, and inconsistencies in the source dataset.
  • Descriptive Insights : Summarizes key patterns and relationships in housing prices and property features.
  • Predictive Performance : Evaluates the accuracy of the price prediction model using standard metrics.
description: Insights into Housing Prices and Forecasting Performance
